				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well heres my case, I just dont get it. Mages to me are really left out of the spot light, heres why.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Druid -- Dire Charm, Complete Heals, Better Nukes, Snare, Root, Can Melee.
<br />

<br />
Necromancer -- Cackling bones  (and others) , Feign Death, DoTs, Good pet, Mez, Snare, Invis to Undead, Rez, Corpse find.
<br />

<br />
Mage -- Not as good of nukes, Pet suffers with DC, We can summon....
<br />

