<br />
Because the magician class gave up all defensive ability to have the monster pet to defend him. Our pets are everything to us. No class is more reliant on the mage. hell, they have us killing him now just to gain mana (Elemental draw/Siphon). Magician pets were very powerful and could protect the mage, as well as take a beating while the mage burned down the mob. Remember getting an add, and having to decide whether or not you could beat them both or had to run for the hills?  Those days are over...one add = certain death in GoD.
<br />

<br />
They will not give us the power we once had, they need to give us some defense. 
<br />
At any rate, that is why we SHOULD have the best pets. Hell we should have 4 to choose from (not counting MS4 since next to no one has it), they should be the best at what they do.
<br />

