<br />

<br />
Simply because Magicians offer 2 things really, nukes and a pet.  We have very little utility as a group member.   We have absolutely no defenses.  We can only GATE out of a bad situation.  Over 5 years later and a level 4 spell is our only defense.  Our only group abilities are T-rods, DS, and CoH (which is hardly ever used now days).
<br />

<br />
Beastlords can SLOW, a huge advantage to any group.  BL can off-tank, melee, and with enough AA's do a very good job of it.  In many areas, a BL can use SLOW to get aggro and melee as primary tank.  They even get SoW at some point, making it possible for the pet to hold off the bad guys while the BL can try to run. <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="wink" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Necros have an obscene amount of defense.  They have Roots, Snares, Fear, can mez/slow undead, and of course they have <span style="font-weight: bold">FD</span> to save them.  And hey, if that doesn't work, they can summon their corpse to zoneline and rez themselves!  Necros don't have as many group buffs as BL, but they do have things like MIND WRACK which is a huge GROUP ability.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">What instead makes more sense is that pet + other stuff for all three classes, if we had a perfect system for scoring both, should be roughly equal among all three.
<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Well the arguement here is PET + GROUP ABILITYS + DPS + DEFENSE.
<br />

<br />
So lets score them now and make up numbers.
<br />

<br />
Defense- necro (100), BL (60), mage (10)
<br />
DPS - Mage (100), Necro (90), BL (70)
<br />
Group abilitys - BL (100), Necro (60), Mage (40) 
<br />
PET - Mage (100), BL (80), Necro (70) 
<br />

<br />
Necro 320
<br />
BL 310
<br />
Mage 250
<br />

<br />
And that is why I feel magicians should have the BEST pets, because we rank so low in the other categories of Defense and Group abilities.<br />_________________<br /><DIV *****"position:relative; width=80%; filter:glow(color=FF0000)"><a *****"font-weight:bold; color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration: none" href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796  target="new-window"><b>Lord Zacatac Soulwanderer</b></a></div>"1450 Club" Tradeskiller
