				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mage pets need to be able to off tank WITHOUT the mob being slowed, because we can't slow the mobs. The pet is our defense it HAS to do this or we have none but gating. Over powered? Not at all, it is why we have no defense as in:
<br />

<br />
Root: NO
<br />
Snare: NO
<br />
Feign Death: NO
<br />
Res: NO
<br />
Summon Corpse: NO
<br />
Rune Skin: NO
<br />
Invunerability: NO
<br />
Levant to zone in: NO
<br />
Mind Wrack: NO (they don't hurt their pet for extra mana, we do)
<br />
Self Heals (Life Taps, healing dots): NO
<br />
Best Mana Regen in the Game: NO
<br />
Pets: Yes
<br />
Gate: Yes
<br />

<br />

<br />
That is mainly why mages feel we deserve and were told we would have the best pets. We gave up a ton for Offense with little to no defense. If your wondering why I mentioned Levant, well it is a better defense then gate. Your at zone in, and you run back, unlike gate where you have to cross from where you bound to get back. A huge difference. We have no viable forms of defense if you can't gate, but our pet.  Gate though it can save you from needing a res, many mages will forgo the gate and take a res, because running back takes too long.
<br />

<br />
If your wondering about offense, remember necro dots while they take time to work, they have the abilities to let them,and their DPS over time is amoung the best in the game, if not the best. Their pets will dish out a lot of DPS and with their mana regen can keep dot after dot after dot on the mobs. A lot of utility, a lot of DPS and very little draw backs. In the original EQ the main draw back was they were KOS in most places. That is no longer true. They have all the benifits of being a KOS class in most original zones in the game, but now play a game where that is no longer a draw back or even an issue.
<br />

<br />
Just for clarification, the mage class gives up ALL of the above for the best pets and the 2nd best nuke in the game. The pets shouldn't be 10%-15% better than others, but at least 50% or more.
<br />

<br />
Calebe<br />_________________<br />Level 70 Magician
<br />
E'CI Server
<br />
Infinit</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
