				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Magistix wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I never said Mage pets had to be the best. But they should be good since we dont do tons of damage or have snare and so on</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
I'm curious as to what level magician you play and at what level of the game progression wise?  I do more damage than any other class consistantly against most encounters (barring high resist / mana drain) than anyone in my Time / pre-Qvic-GoD guild, and since my guild really geared up I have not been outdamaged in any grind group I parsed (I almost always parse damage in grind groups if I can) by anyone ever.  With OoW I'm beating everyone by a really big margin; though our wizards don't have their good spells yet (On supernatural guardian and avatar of elements combined, I delt 84,000 damage vs our top wizards 54,000...~54% more, ~420 dps average, he landed 3 less nukes than I did, so, not enough to make it up even if all crit).  
<br />
 
<br />
Once other classes start getting ahold of their spells they'll start doing very well I'm sure.   Even so, I think at the moment the ONLY two places our class is particularly lacking are (aside from broken oow spells and the joke they call epic 1.5) pet damage via focus items (and pet focus scaling in general) and pet healing.  In my opinion, the higher teir focus items just aren't doing enough over the DPoC on the new pets.  None of the new pets are doing enough damage after pet focuses are applied, especially on higher teir focuses.  Also, Minion of Eternity went from a 35% hp upgrade over unfocused on the 61 pet to a 12% hp upgrade over unfocused on the 66 pet; the disparity is ever larger on higher teir focuses (48% vs 18% on MoDiscord!!!!).  This needs to be changed.  I don't think I really need to comment on our pet heals heh...we all know.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370607" target="_blank" class="postlink">Magus Tiiden Vandorgriffin</a>
<br />
70 Magician, Rodcet Nife</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
